ad to - do it you see, and - me}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3279529\charrsid12135944 
 and - sister next o - me would go home from school and - build the copper and light the fire and get the water ready for them to wash. Then next morning they'd leave 'em in a bath 
of cold water, we had to get up and - blue them, starch 'em and put 'em on the line before we went to school.
