She lived while I was little, yes, up 'til I was ten then she went back to Portsmouth, she died in Portsmouth. Be about nine when she went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14642234 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3279529\charrsid12135944 What age did you put yourself to bed?
