Well I should be - say - how old would I be - when I was ten - used to go with him when he went he early and I had to go - by ten, he used to go early then, perhaps seven - seven or eight o'clock, no larger than eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14642234 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3279529\charrsid12135944 
How old were you when you put yourself to bed without being put by anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3434615 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3279529\charrsid12135944 I should be that age. Yes, ten.
