I should be - seven when I went to Queens Walk, I went then. Yes. Don't remember much of that school, that's funny isn't it. There was a girl got kidnapped from there, that school. Mm. Seagar her name was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14642234 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3279529\charrsid12135944 Didn't they say it was a put up job?
