They said it was, when she come home they had in the parlour and people paid to go in to have a look at her. She lived next door to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14642234 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3279529\charrsid12135944 And you paid to look at the girl?
